body_text:
Recently, @relud added support for running the contract tests during deploys. Failures in the contract tests will mark a deploy as failed, and are generally much nicer than finding the same problems after the deploy.
This PR adds a test that checks the /__heartbeat__ endpoint of the server, which contains several internal checks.
@chartjes r?

